sentences: Natasha Paremski (born May 11, 1987) is a Russian-American classical pianist.
Natasha Paremski was born in Moscow, Russia.
She studied at the Andreyev School of Music (Детская музыкальная школа имени В.В.Андреева) in Moscow with Nina Valentinovna Malikova at the age of 4 before moving to the United States.
She studied with Pavlina Dokovska at Mannes College of Music, from which she graduated in 2007.
